then you have kunark with the eception of FV, Lake, DL and KC its all darky. onpopulated zones are chardok, SkyFire, Kaesora, HS, CoM and EJ. Then Lightys have Velius cept for the ocational raids in Velketors, CS, ToFS, etc but its pretty safe for lighties there. And atlast antonica ... its realy devided to many zones to mention but usualy the zones close to the lighty or darky cities are owned by them. <br>
<br>
The highend guilds situation well there are only 3 notable lighty guilds on VZ doing ToV and raiding sleepers and killing statue. There are also 2 Darky guilds, then you have one notacible 4 teaming guild left after prophets went up in smoke(the used to win the best of bests). There are many more guilds raiding plains and stuff but these five guilds I must say are the highest and I think it points out the power balance between the teams. <br>
<br>
Both sides are pretty Blubie eccept for the occational darky twink roaming in Lake, or ranger harvesting newbie lighties in GF with the PKER shouts echoing between the trees. <br>
But you can if you want interupt both sides while exping to kill them off. But I have as a lighty beeing able to go to kunark on the bloated belly then run to chardock without even beeing attacked on the way even tho there are alot of darkies in OT and manny at my level at SF ent.<br>
<br>
As a 4 teamer I must say you get more PvP then you get in Q3 or the most FPSs, if you want to. hehe and I knew if some darkie would post in this thread they would call the lighties bluebies, they always do... couse they dont play 1 team like them, but to be honest then you wouldnt see any gnomes, dwarvs, highelfs, woodelfs or halfelfs around couse they would be killing eachoter and then you have a 2 team server once again (for the highend of the game(human vs evil))<br>
<br>
well thats my view on vz hopes it helps you in you decision.<br>
